Sila wants to know how to calculate the values using math function.can you please guide her to perform the math Calculations. Note:use the Floor, Ceil, Sqrt, Pow

Sample Input : 76.78
               16
               2
               3
Sample Output:  76
                77
                4
                8   

public class Solution {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
     Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        Float num1 = sc.nextFloat();
        int num2 = sc.nextInt();
        int num3 = sc.nextInt();
        int num4 = sc.nextInt();
        System.out.println((int)Math.floor(num1));
        System.out.println((int)Math.ceil(num1));
        System.out.println((int)Math.sqrt(num2));
        System.out.println((int)Math.pow(num3,num4));
    }
}
